               <msContents>
                  <summary>Psalter, ዳዊት። with the Psalter of the Virgin; መዝሙረ፡ ድንግል።, Image of the Praises of Mary, መልክአ፡ ውዳሴ።; Image of the Gate of Light, መልክዐ፡ አንቀጸ፡ ብርሃን።</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="178v"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT2701Dawit"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1"><locus from="1r" to="136v"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT2000Mazmur"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
